Package: nnmf
Type: Package
Title: Nonnegative Matrix Factorization  
Version: 1.0
Date: 2026-01-06
Authors@R: person("Michail", "Tsagris", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "mtsagris@uoc.gr")
Author: Michail Tsagris [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Michail Tsagris <mtsagris@uoc.gr>
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports: ClusterR, Matrix, parallel, Rfast, Rfast2, Rglpk, sparcl, stats 
Description: Nonegative matrix factorization (NMF). Parallel computing is an option to enhance the speed and high-dimensional and large scale (and/or sparse) data are allowed. Relevant papers include: Cutler and Breiman (1994), <doi:10.1080/00401706.1994.10485840> and Wang, Yang, Qin and Zha (2008), <doi:10.1145/1390156.1390298>.  
License: GPL (>= 2)

